metadata.description: Time for Vim!'s second mp3 release, and it's a stand-out piece of totally original 'electronic music', poised anywhere between breakbeat, idm, and triphop. Definitions really don't make sense in this case - let's just say this wouldn't be out of place on Rephlex or Skam. Watch the trademark Follin-esque oblique Vim! chords too.. mm, retrocreamygoodness..
metadata.title: Vim! - Whirlwind Snooker [mtw007]
